    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities\n\n`powerhouse/builder-profile` (12 ops) defines individual contributor identities in the Powerhouse ecosystem. This is the model that `ServiceOffering.operatorId` references via PHID \u2014 the operator who creates and manages a service offering.\n\n## Cross-Model References\n\n- ServiceOffering.`operatorId: PHID` \u2192 BuilderProfile (the offering's operator)\n- Referenced by [[builders model aggregates builder collections]] as individual entries\n- Part of the Organization & Identity zone alongside [[network-profile model represents network-level organizational entities]] and [[operational-hub-profile model defines operational hub configurations]]\n\nSince [[service-offering model defines tiered pricing with option groups and service groups]], the operatorId PHID creates a cross-zone dependency from Service & Pricing to Organization & Identity.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:28.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:28.000Z"
    }
  },
